snippet.title: PARSEC47 Extreme Difficulty Gameplay
snippet.description: PARSEC47 is open-source-software by Japanese developer Kenta Cho. It can be downloaded from his website, ABA games, here: http://www.asahi-net.or.jp/~cs8k-cyu/windows/p47_e.html or installed via your Linux package manager.
